# CSRF Agent v2 example .env
# Copy the block you want into a real .env (or rename this file to .env).
# scripts/go.sh will auto-load .env at runtime.
#
# Required:
#   - TARGET
#   - LLM_PROVIDER (and provider API key)
# Optional:
#   - CREDENTIALS (JSON, form-encoded, or cookie notes the agent can use)
#
# Ensure gospider and curl are installed and on PATH.

########################################
# Profile: OpenAI (default model gpt-5)
########################################
# TARGET="https://your-app.example"
# CREDENTIALS='{"username":"alice","password":"secret"}'
# LLM_PROVIDER=openai
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-REPLACE_ME
# OPENAI_MODEL=gpt-5

########################################
# Profile: Anthropic (default Sonnet 4.5)
